0.0.1.name: wordpress/opengrapher
0.0.1.description:
OpenGrapher is based on This Post by Yoast.

The plugin allows you to add the following official badges:

  • Facebook Like/Send
  • Twitter Tweet
  • Google +1
  • LinkedIn Share
  • StumbleUpon's Stumble

Additionally, it will track clicks with Google Analytics and/or Clicky. It automatically detects if they're present.

You can see the plugin in action on Gunner Technology's website.

For any more questions, please go to Gunner Technology's post: OpenGrapher: WordPress Plugin that Adds and Tracks Social Sharing and leave a comment.
